name: LoL5
body:
### Welcome to LoL5 Home Page.
LoL5 is an android app that lets you follow up to 5 summoners and lets you know when they have started a game,
so then you know it's time to log in and join them for the next one or maybe spectate their current game.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with app or web page? [contact support](lol5supp@gmail.com) and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
